<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy | BookMyStay</title>
  
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff7e5f, #feb47b);
            color: #333;
        }
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007bff, #0056b3);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: bold;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-bottom: 5px solid #ff7e5f;
        }
        main {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 30px;
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #ff7e5f;
            border-bottom: 4px solid #ff7e5f;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding-left: 0;
        }
        ul li {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            margin: 12px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 6px solid #ff7e5f;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
            color: #0056b3;
        }
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007bff, #0056b3);
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        Privacy Policy
    </header>
    
    <main>
        <section>
            <h2>Effective Date: </h2>
            <p>Welcome to <strong>BookMyStay</strong>! Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our platform.</p>
        </section>
        
        <section>
            <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email, phone number, and payment details when you register or book a stay.</li>
                <li><strong>Listing Information:</strong> If you are an owner, we collect details about your property, including location, pricing, and availability.</li>
                <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information about how you interact with our website.</li>
                <li><strong>Cookies & Tracking Technologies:</strong> Used to enhance user experience and analyze trends.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        
        <section>
            <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>We use your information for the following purposes:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>To facilitate bookings and provide customer support.</li>
                <li>To process payments securely.</li>
                <li>To personalize user experience and provide relevant recommendations.</li>
                <li>To ensure security and prevent fraud.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        
        <section>
            <h2>3. Sharing of Information</h2>
            <p>We do not sell or rent your personal information. However, we may share data with:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> Payment processors, hosting providers, and analytics services.</li>
                <li><strong>Legal Authorities:</strong> When required by law to protect our rights.</li>
                <li><strong>Owners & Renters:</strong> Limited information shared to facilitate booking transactions.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>
    
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> BookMyStay. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
